briefdescription.para: tests ssh_config_parse_file with multiple Port settings.
Verify the new options are passed from configuration.
Verify the authentication methods from configuration are effective.
Verify the configuration parser does not choke on unknown or unsupported configuration options.
Verify the configuration parser accepts Match keyword with full OpenSSH syntax.
Verify we can parse ProxyJump configuration option.
Verify the configuration parser handles all the possible versions of RekeyLimit configuration option.
